Tables


\begin{tabular}[pos]{table spec}
...table here...
\end{tabular}

The table spec argument tells LaTeX the alignment to be used in each column and the vertical lines to insert
The optional parameter pos can be used to specify the vertical position of the table relative to the baseline of the surrounding text



Creating a Simple Table in LaTeX
\begin{center}
\begin{tabular}{ c c c }
