 4 & 5 & 6 \\  
 7 & 8 & 9    
\end{tabular}
\end{center}

The tabular environment is the default LaTeX method to create tables.
You must specify a parameter here we use {c c c} which tells LaTeX there are three columns and the text inside each one of them must be centered.

