Aligning Equations with amsmath

The amsmath package provides a handful of options for displaying equations.
You can choose the layout that better suits your document.

\begin{equation} \label{eq1}
\begin{split}
A & = \frac{\pi r^2}{2} \\
 & = \frac{1}{2} \pi r^2
\end{split}
\end{equation}
